  <h3 style="color: #CC0000">HOTEL IDEAL TOWER</h3>          
The Hotel Ideal Tower is a 4-star hotel located away from the city noise and is just 2 km away from the Railway Station. To make the guests feel comfortable, the hotel offers a high bandwidth internet. It gives the business travelers an option to work easily anywhere in the hotel. The hotel offers guests with elegant rooms for a comfortable stay. Laundry services are also available in the rooms. The hotel is equipped with an in-house shopping arcade that offers a wide variety of handlooms and other artifacts. An in-house bakery is also available in the hotel that serves mouth watering goodies.

<h3 style="color: #CC0000">HOTEL PRAGYA</h3>
Hotel Pragya is a budget hotel located in Allahabad. This hotel is a haven for comfort and luxury. Travelers or visitor who is looking for budget hotels, this is the ideal place to stay. The rooms at this hotel are spacious and well furnished with Indian traditional system. Whoever stays here feels homely as it is called as comfort hub. Facilities at this hotel are awesome which includes 24 hours room service, hot and cold running water facilities along with Rasoi restaurant which serves Indian food. 

<h3 style="color: #CC0000">HOTEL SIDDHARTH</h3>
Hotel Siddharth is located on Vidyapeeth Road, making it strategically located in the heart of Varanasi. It is at a walking distance form Sankat Mochan Hanuman Temple. This 3-star property can be reached from Varanasi Junction Railway station or Varanasi Bus Depot both within 3 km of radius. A quick cab drive will be handy from Lal Bahadur Shastri International Airport about 24 km from hotel.
Hotel is in close proximity to Harishchandra Ghat, Panchganga Ghat and Hanuman Ghat to experience the beauty of Ganges. To explore the rich local culture of Varanasi, stroll into the famous Dashswamedh Market, Thatheri Bazaar and Vishwanath Road Market.Some of the must visit places in Varanasi are – Kashi Vishwanath Temple, Ramnagar Fort, Sigra Church, Dhamek Stupa and Sarnath Museum. The city of Ghats, Banaras hosts famous Manikarnika Ghat, Dasaswamedh Ghat and Assi Ghat to experience the vast River Ganges. Bharat Kala Bhavan Museum, is a must visit place.For leisure time of guests, hotel has maintained a clean outdoor pool.

